<div class="big_wrapper">
  <div class="wrapper" id="one">
    <div class="point_copy">
      <h3 class="center">
        What is Advlo?
      </h3>
      <p>
        Advlo is a global network that empowers locals and travelers to connect through adventures. With this platform, people from around the world will be able to easily share, market and sell their expertise for the adventures they love directly to travelers. Advlo travelers will enjoy access to far more personal, engaging and culturally authentic adventures than what is currently being offered by tour operators.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="point_copy">
      <h3 class="center">
        Lets Break It Down...
